sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as User
  participant UI as Web UI
  participant K as Kong Gateway
  participant AU as Auth Service
  participant PR as Profile Service
  participant AI as AI Assistance
  participant PP as Plan and Payment
  participant SQL as SQL shared cluster
  participant MG as Mongo shared cluster
  participant S3 as S3
  participant PG as Payment Gateway
  participant GPT as GPT API

  Note over SQL: Same cluster different tables credentials users plans orders payments document_meta
  Note over MG: Same cluster different collections user_details static_questions ai_session

  Note over U,GPT: 1 Signup and profile
  U->>UI: Sign up
  UI->>K: POST /api/v1/auth/signup
  K->>AU: forward
  AU->>SQL: INSERT credentials table
  AU->>PR: POST internal create user
  PR->>SQL: INSERT users table
  PR->>MG: INSERT user_details collection
  PR-->>AU: 201
  AU-->>UI: success

  Note over U,GPT: 2 Login JWT
  U->>UI: Log in
  UI->>K: POST /api/v1/auth/login
  K->>AU: forward
  AU->>SQL: SELECT credentials table
  AU-->>UI: JWT access token

  Note over U,GPT: 3 Profile me
  UI->>K: GET /api/v1/users/me JWT
  K->>PR: forward
  PR->>SQL: SELECT users table
  PR->>MG: FIND user_details by user_id
  PR-->>UI: profile JSON

  Note over U,GPT: 4 Plans catalog
  UI->>K: GET /api/v1/plans JWT
  K->>PP: forward
  PP->>SQL: SELECT plans table
  PP-->>UI: plans list

  Note over U,GPT: 5 Static questions by group
  UI->>K: GET /api/v1/questions JWT
  K->>AI: forward
  AI->>MG: FIND static_questions by user group
  AI-->>UI: questions

  Note over U,GPT: 6 AI chat
  UI->>K: POST /api/v1/ai/chat JWT
  K->>AI: forward
  AI->>GPT: completion request
  GPT-->>AI: model text
  AI->>MG: UPSERT ai_session collection
  AI-->>UI: answer

  Note over U,GPT: 7 Resume PDF presign parse
  UI->>K: POST /api/v1/documents/upload-url JWT
  K->>AI: forward
  AI->>SQL: INSERT document_meta table PENDING
  AI-->>UI: presigned URL documentId
  UI->>S3: PUT resume PDF
  AI->>AI: parse job reads S3
  AI->>SQL: UPDATE document_meta READY plus JSON pointer

  Note over U,GPT: 8 Order and pay
  UI->>K: POST /api/v1/orders JWT
  K->>PP: forward
  PP->>SQL: INSERT orders table
  PP->>PG: create checkout
  PG-->>PP: pay session
  PP-->>UI: checkout URL
  PG->>K: POST webhook signed
  K->>PP: forward
  PP->>SQL: UPDATE orders INSERT payments tables
  PP-->>PG: 200 OK
